ruleset.description:
Default PMD ruleset shipped by the pipelines library. Focuses on unused code detection rules from the bestpractices category.
Usage in Gradle (build.gradle.kts): pmd { ruleSetFiles = files("path/to/pipelines/global/scripts/languages/java/pmd/pmd-ruleset.xml") }
Usage in Maven (pom.xml): <plugin><artifactId>maven-pmd-plugin</artifactId> <configuration><rulesets><ruleset>path/to/pmd-ruleset.xml</ruleset></rulesets></configuration></plugin>
